channel.title: Comments on: Day 6 – The Czech Republic – Austria – Slovakia

item.title: By: steve
item.dc:creator: steve
item.description: I can sympathise with your vehicular problems. Stuck on Oxford Circus yesterday with no gears is no fun. Looks like you are seeing some amazing places. Happy trucking on Day 7 and beyond. Hope A&E can stay the course.
